    "The United States and India are the second most citing partners, with a link strength of 30.",
    "The United States and Australia are the third most citing partners, with a link strength of 25.",
    "In terms of citation network, the United States has the largest network, with 35 links.",
    "India and China are tied for second place, with 30 links each.",
    "The citation network analysis of journals revealed that the largest citation network consisted of 22 journals citing each other frequently (Figure 4D)."
